CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - Allegheny County Squad - Coached by Joe McCune of Scott High School, North Braddock, and Mario Martorelli of North Hills High School, this hand-picked Allegheny County array of aces will give a solid accounting of themselves Saturday night, in the 14th annual Jaycee football classic... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Allegheny County All-Star Jaycee football team with coaches Joe McCune and Mario Martorelli, posed on field
